title: KeenRush and the Keen 6 Box
content:
I may be screwing up old memories, but bear with me here...

It seems to me that many moons ago, when Forge315 aka JosephBurke was preparing to leave, he post-mailed his ultra-rare Commander Keen: Aliens ate my Babysitter gamebox to KeenRush, and KeenRush promised to upload beautiful scans of it in a week or two.

Needless to say, those scans never arrived.

What happened?--------------------
[url=http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/]Cerebral Cortex 314[/url] - For All of your Commander Keen Needs.
[url=http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/dave/joes.html]Eat at Joes[/url]
